Package: xtsum
Type: Package
Title: Summary Statistics for Panel Data
Version: 0.1.0
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0), knitr, magrittr, rlang, plm
Imports: dplyr, kableExtra, sampleSelection
Author: Joao Claudio Macosso 
Maintainer: <joaoclaudiomacosso@gmail.com>
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Description: xtsum is an R wrapper based on STATA's xtsum command, it is used to compute summary statistics for a panel data set. It generates overall, between-group, and within-group statistics for specified variables in a panel data set.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
